\">h.Cer.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">276</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: in a concrete sense, as though external to the body, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κάλλεϊ μέν οἱ πρῶτα προσώπατα καλὰ κάθηρεν ἀμβροσίῳ, οἵῳ Κυθέρεια Χρίεται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:18:192\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.192</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: freq. i&lt;*&gt; Trag. and Prose, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">γυναῖκε . . κάλλει ἀμώμω</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg002.perseus-grc1:185\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pers.\">Pers.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">185</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κ. σώματος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0161.tlg001:105\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Democr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">105</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἶσχος</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg011.perseus-grc1:201a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Smp.\">Smp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">201a</biblScope> </bibl>: in a general sense, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τῶν ἔργων τῷ μεγέθει καὶ τῷ κάλλει Χαλεπὸν ἐξισῶσαι τοὺς ἐπαίνους</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0010.tlg021.perseus-grc1:36\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Isoc.\">Isoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.36</bib